& [MathProcessingToolScripts] is the project-local runtime surface for finite mathematical processing
  + [canonical_specification_uuid] is 6d872555-3e20-4f30-83dd-053590a7bc25
  + [source_snapshot_uuid] is 92611a3d-0cbb-437c-8cce-53e12aa6630c
